OL,3,CMum who lost her son to suicide calls
OL,4,Cfor change
OL,6,FThe mother of a Borders teenager who
OL,7,Ftook his own life after being treated
OL,8,Fin an adult mental health unit has
OL,9,Fasked the Scottish government to
OL,10,Fimprove access to specialist services
OL,11,Ffor young people.
OL,13,FJane Macdonell says her son Harris was
OL,14,F"traumatised" after receiving
OL,15,Ftreatment at NHS Borders' Huntlyburn
OL,16,FHouse and believes access to a young
OL,17,Fperson's mental health ward could have
OL,18,Fsaved his life.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@MO]
