OL,6,FMental health Minister Maree Todd, who
OL,7,Fmet with the family at Holyrood, said
OL,8,Fshe would now take time to reflect on
OL,9,Fwhat she'd heard.
OL,11,FHarris was 19 when he took his own
OL,12,Flife in the summer of 2020.
OL,14,FWhen he was 16 years old he was
OL,15,Fadmitted to NHS Border's adult ward
OL,16,Fafter experiencing a mental health
OL,17,Fcrisis. He was later diagnosed with
OL,18,Fautism and ADHD.
