OL,6,FWhen he became unwell again during
OL,7,Fcovid, his mum says he struggled to
OL,8,Faccess medical help.
OL,10,FJane Macdonnel, said: "He had lost all
OL,11,Ftrust in the people that had put him
OL,12,Fin the adult unit."
OL,14,FShe added: "I think the experience of
OL,15,FHuntlyburn set him on a path in his
OL,16,Frelationship with mental health
OL,17,Fservices that we could not change.
OL,26,@rD@WOUvD@LOU
