OL,6,F"I think that a young person who is
OL,7,Facutely unwell needs to be in a place
OL,8,Fwhere they feel safe and they may not
OL,9,Fbe able to articulate that to anybody
OL,10,Fat that time, but we as adults as
OL,11,Fprofessionals know the sort of
OL,12,Fenvironments that are going to make
OL,13,Fyoung people feel safer and that
OL,14,Fthey're in a place that is age
OL,15,Fappropriate that has the staff that
OL,16,Fare trained."
