OL,6,FMaree Todd, Minister for Social Care,
OL,7,FWellbeing and Sport, said: "I have to
OL,8,Fsay their story was really difficult
OL,9,Fto hear. I guess I'm going to need to
OL,10,Ftake time to reflect on what I have
OL,11,Fheard and to think about how we can
OL,12,Fincorporate that into our work as a
OL,13,Fgovernment.
