OL,6,F"We talked about the existing capacity
OL,7,Fin terms of mental health beds for
OL,8,Fyoung people, the proposals to
OL,9,Fincrease the intensive care capacity
OL,10,Fthat's available and we also talked
OL,11,Fabout how we're keen to develop
OL,12,Fintensive home support for people who
OL,13,Fmight be in the situation that Harris
OL,14,Fwas in."
OL,16,FAfter Harris's death, the family
OL,17,Fcalled for a Fatal Accident Inquiry to
OL,18,Fbe held into his treatment at NHS
OL,19,FBorders. Jane believes there are still
OL,20,Fquestions to be answered.
