OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Crown Office
OL,7,Fand Procurator Fiscal Service said
OL,8,Ftheir investigation was "ongoing" and
OL,9,Fthat "significant progress" is being
OL,10,Fmade.
OL,12,FA statement from NHS Borders said:
OL,13,F"Whilst in order to respect
OL,14,Fconfidentiality we will not comment in
OL,15,Fdetail, we can confirm that following
OL,16,FHarris's tragic death an extensive and
OL,17,Fexternally led review of his care was
OL,18,Fundertaken so that we could learn any
OL,19,Flessons to improve our services in the
OL,20,Ffuture.
