OL,6,F"The actions identified by the review
OL,7,Fhave been implemented.
OL,9,F"We agree that children and young
OL,10,Fpeople who require inpatient care
OL,11,Fshould, wherever possible, be admitted
OL,12,Fto an age-appropriate unit.
OL,14,F"If this is not possible, and they
OL,15,Fhave to be admitted to our adult
OL,16,Finpatient unit, we will always advise
OL,17,Fthe Mental Welfare Commission (MWC)
OL,18,Fthat this has happened, in line with
OL,19,Ftheir guidance.
