OL,6,F"Our practice is then informed by the
OL,7,FMWC for Scotland guidance on treating
OL,8,Fchildren and young people in adult
OL,9,Fmental health wards."
OL,11,FThere are 48 NHS specialist beds for
OL,12,Fadolescents in Scotland - in
OL,13,FEdinburgh, Glasgow and Dundee- plus a
OL,14,Ffurther six for those under 12 in the
OL,15,FRoyal Hospital for Sick Children in
OL,16,FGlasgow.
OL,18,FA recent report from the Mental
OL,19,FWelfare Commission shows there were 79
OL,20,Fadmissions to adult wards, involving
OL,21,F66 young people, in 2022-23.
