OL,6,FCharity in Harris' memory
OL,8,FJane and her husband Dave launched
OL,9,FHarris Trust in their son's memory.
OL,11,FHe was a talented accordion player and
OL,12,Fin his early years at Lilliesleaf
OL,13,FPrimary School in Melrose he thrived
OL,14,Fand showed talent in sports, playing
OL,15,Ftennis for Melrose and rugby for the
OL,16,FSelkirk Rhinos.
