OL,6,FNow, the charity organises sports
OL,7,Fevents and music workshops in a number
OL,8,Fof secondary schools in the Borders to
OL,9,Fwork with young people who need extra
OL,10,Fsupport and to raise awareness about
OL,11,Fneurodiversity.
OL,13,FSam Johnston, who runs the music
OL,14,Fproject for the trust, said: "Learning
OL,15,Fabout what happened to Harris I just
OL,16,Ffelt there was so much more that we
OL,17,Fcould be doing to help people who go
OL,18,Fthrough those same struggles.
